265
00:30:57,880 --> 00:30:59,840
So, so.

266
00:31:01,080 --> 00:31:03,040
Vielen Dank auch.

267
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:06,840
Herein!

268
00:31:12,320 --> 00:31:16,240
